comment: Valanciunas (TOR) makes incidental contact with Stephenson (MEM) during rebounding.
Barnes (MEM) intentionally kicks the ball on the play.
Valanciunas (TOR) sets the screen on Stephenson (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Stephenson (MEM) makes contact with DeRozan (TOR) that affects his FOM away from the ball.
Carter (MEM) moves his pivot foot. The official is looking for any potential illegal contact and does not pick up the pivot foot.
Biyombo (TOR) and Randolph (MEM) briefly engage and separate during rebounding.
Biyombo (TOR) sets the screen on Conley (MEM) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Biyombo (TOR) maintains legal guarding position as he defends Conley's (MEM) jump shot attempt. Any contact on the play is initiated by Conley.
Barnes (MEM) commits a take foul on Biyombo (TOR).
Carter (MEM) makes contact with Patterson (TOR) after he secures the rebound.
Randolph (MEM) sets the screen on Joseph (TOR) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
LHH shows that Biyombo (TOR) maintains legal guarding position and makes incidental contact with Conley (MEM) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
